title: Public Comment Sought on Proposed Changes to Code of Judicial Ethics (Supreme Court of California) ...
text: ( Source : Supreme Court of California ) About the Committee The Supreme Court established the Committee on Judicial Ethics Opinions (CJEO) to help inform the judiciary and the public about judicial ethics. (Cal. Rules of Court , rule 9.80.)
